data.description: Discover an elegant residence featuring three spacious bedrooms, three well-appointed bathrooms, and a master suite boasting a luxurious bathtub, separate shower area, and a generously-sized walk-in closet. The expansive living room offers stylish shelves and a designated space for your TV, complemented by a modern electric fireplace. The kitchen and bathroom vanities showcase exquisite granite countertops, complemented by a tasteful backsplash beneath the cabinets. Culinary enthusiasts will appreciate the large pantry in the kitchen. The double-car garage, equipped with a door opener, adds convenience to your daily routine. Step outside to a beautifully landscaped front yard and a charming backyard with a pergola illuminated by electric lights at night. The pergola's ceramic floor enhances its aesthetic, and the backyard features synthetic grass for easy maintenance. This home is a showcase of numerous thoughtful upgrades.
